			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Make a backup of the database and execute the following SQL request in the console or in phpmysqladmin:
<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Code:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="code">update phpbb_words set replacement=concat&#40;'http&#58;//',word,'.bbspam.com/'&#41;;</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />
This command changes the censorship table. For each <span style="font-style: italic">word </span> the replacement is &quot;http://<span style="font-style: italic">word</span>.bbspam.com/&quot;.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
